images.alt: A large, ornate chandelier made of gold-colored rectangular metallic pieces, hanging from a chain in a dimly lit room.
A large chandelier made of stacked green glass pieces hangs from a metallic ceiling.
A dark hallway with an elegant green chandelier hanging from the ceiling.
A dark room with wooden walls, a gold circular chandelier hanging from the ceiling, a round gold rug on the floor, and a large black-framed mirror or window on the back wall.
A large, ornate chandelier with multiple tiers of glass or crystal elements hanging from a ceiling with a dark, textured surface.
Luxurious bedroom with a large bed on a furry rug, dark walls, floral artwork, a gold chandelier on the ceiling, a fan on a tripod stand, and a window with curtains.
Close-up of purple and green plants with water droplets on the leaves and falling droplets in the background
An outdoor seating area with modern chairs and a patio umbrella, behind a green wall with succulents and hanging plants.
Outdoor patio area with a glass dining table, six chairs with cushions, and two small side tables, surrounded by greenery and a pool in the background.
A woman with platinum blonde hair and makeup lying on a plush green cushion, wearing a richly embroidered floral jacket with fur trim.

A bedroom with a bed placed under a sloped ceiling, featuring dark wooden walls on either side and a green marble-textured wall behind the headboard. The bed has light-colored bedding, pillows, and a fluffy beige rug at the foot, with a window above
A bedroom with a sloped ceiling, a large bed with beige bedding and pillows, a small bedside table, a window with natural light, and a plush area rug on the floor.
A cozy bedroom with a bed featuring dark brown and white pillows, a furry blanket, large windows allowing natural light, and a sloped ceiling with marble and wooden paneling.
Close-up of a fluffy, cream-colored sheep's wool with a background featuring peeled pineapple slices.
A vintage wooden bedside table with a single drawer, set against a marbled wall with green and brown veins.
Black leather chair with four wooden legs isolated on white background.
Black leather armchair with wooden legs, featuring a curved backrest and armrests with decorative stitching details.
Black leather chair with four legs, view from back, isolated on white background.

<style>
/* FORCE Squarespace code block to behave */
.sqs-block-code {
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;

}

.sqs-block-content {
  padding: 0 !important;
  margin: 0 !important;
}

/* Wrapper - FORCE collapse and contain */
#tenebre-gallery-nav-wrapper {
  position: relative !important;
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  background: transparent;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  min-height: auto !important;
  height: auto !important;
  display: block !important;
}

/* Navigation Container - FORCE inside wrapper */
#tenebre-gallery-nav {
  position: relative !important;
  top: 0 !important;
  left: 0 !important;
  right: 0 !important;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto !important;
  padding: 25px 20px !important;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 60px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  z-index: 50;
  transform: none !important;
}

/* Gallery Button */
.tenebre-nav-btn {
  position: relative;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 16px 24px;
  transition: all 0.5s ease;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: tenebreButtonFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards;
}

.tenebre-nav-btn:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
